OL,3,CNissan staff learn British Sign
OL,4,CLanguage to communicate with deaf
OL,5,Ccolleagues
OL,7,FJulia Barthram went to meet the team
OL,8,Fat Nissan who have been learning
OL,9,FBritish Sign Language
OL,11,FWorkers at Nissan have started
OL,12,Flearning British Sign Language (BSL)
OL,13,Fto make members of their team who are
OL,14,Fdeaf feel more included.
OL,16,FFour members of the bumper paint shop
OL,17,Fteam are deaf - which makes
OL,18,Fcommunication a challenge. Colleagues
OL,19,Fon their shift asked to learn BSL,
OL,20,Fwith the entire shift volunteering for
OL,21,Fthe training.
