OL,5,Ccolleagues
OL,7,FMicheal Connolly, one of the deaf
OL,8,Foperators, said: "I think it's great,
OL,9,Fit's brilliant because previously no
OL,10,Fone could sign. But now they are keen
OL,11,Fto learn sign language and that makes
OL,12,Fothers in my team want to learn it too.
OL,14,F"This makes it much easier for us deaf
OL,15,Fcolleagues. Communication previously
OL,16,Frelied on lip reading, which is very
OL,17,Fdifficult, but now, it's much easier
OL,18,Ffor us to communicate."
