OL,3,CNissan staff learn British Sign
OL,4,CLanguage to communicate with deaf
OL,5,Ccolleagues
OL,7,FInitially, ten members of the team
OL,8,Fwent on an eleven-week course to learn
OL,9,Fthe basics and they have been sharing
OL,10,Ftheir skills with others to boost
OL,11,Fcommunication and help people feel
OL,12,Fmore included.
OL,14,FMark Hurst, one of those who took part
OL,15,Fin the course, said: "Learning it, we
OL,16,Fhad some funny times, looking at each
OL,17,Fother, watching each other, you know,
OL,18,Fhow to learn.
