OL,5,Ccolleagues
OL,7,F"Some people took to it quicker than
OL,8,Fothers but we all just worked together
OL,9,Fand we got there in the end."
OL,11,FPaintshop colleague, Joel Baddons,
OL,12,Fadded, "Sometimes people trip up and
OL,13,Fyou can have a bit of a joke about it,
OL,14,Fif you're doing the wrong signs and
OL,15,Fthings like that, but yeah, it's been
OL,16,Freally good as a whole."
OL,18,FOther changes have also been made on-
OL,19,Fsite, including using visual aids in
OL,20,Factivities like training, meetings and
OL,21,Fbriefings.
