OL,7,FMichael Jude, the plant's HR Director,
OL,8,Fsays: "It opens up doors to people who
OL,9,Fmight have thought well we couldn't
OL,10,Fhave had a career in manufacturing but
OL,11,Factually, there are adjustments to be
OL,12,Fmade and things we can do to allow
OL,13,Fthat.
OL,15,F"Hopefully we'll see some really good
OL,16,Ftraction from various different
OL,17,Fcommunities out there.
